<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Jul1931"><font color="red">8 July 1931</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I had offered to lend [my nephew George, son of Charles] my typewriter to learn with and to give him &pound;1 a week for helping me with my notes 3 hours a day &hellip; Eliot and Pinker are today arranging the contract terms for <i>Work in Progress</i> and I have offered American rights to Viking Press </div>
